TMUX CHEATSHEET                     q to close
Leader: Ctrl-b

PANES
 %       Split vertical
 "       Split horizontal
 z       Zoom/unzoom pane
 x       Close pane
 o       Next pane
 q       Show pane numbers

SESSIONS
 a       New session
 s       Browse & switch sessions
 ( )     Previous / next session
 L       Toggle last session
 $       Rename session
 k       Kill current session
 d       Detach session

OTHER
 b       Toggle status bar
 [       Scroll mode
